title: The Age of Adaline. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: April 24th, 2015

Description:

After miraculously remaining 29 years old for almost eight decades, Adaline Bowman (Blake Lively) has lived a solitary existence, never allowing herself to get close to anyone who might reveal her secret. But a chance encounter with charismatic philanthropist Ellis Jones (Michiel Huisman) reignites her passion for life and romance. When a weekend with his parents (Harrison Ford and Kathy Baker) threatens to uncover the truth, Adaline makes a decision that will change her life forever.

Director: Lee Toland Krieger

Writers: J. Mills Goodloe, Salvador Paskowitz

Actors: Blake Lively, Michiel Huisman, Kathy Baker, Amanda Crew, Harrison Ford, Ellen Burstyn

Genre: Drama, Romance
